{"tid":977351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★No Win7！微軟1月最新補丁導致部分Win 7出現網絡問題","createTime":"2019-01-11T06:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T08:25:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"85102c6acc349778f2f8f152af59f295ea657fde","tid":977351,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:26:20.000Z","msg":"IT之家1月10日消息 微軟最近發布了針對Windows 7用戶的1月累積性更新補丁。不幸的是，該更新對使用SMBv2共享的用戶造成了一些問題。 KB4480970更新補丁確實附帶了一系列已知問題，但看起來SMBv2問題在內部測試期間被忽視了<br />\n<br />\n該問題最初是在sysadmin sub-Reddit上分享的，但微軟尚未發布官方聲明。在微軟TechNet論壇的另一篇帖子中，用戶抱怨KB4480970補丁會導致Windows 2008 R2服務器出現問題。到目前為止唯一的解決方法是從系統中卸載該更新。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/405/020.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F405%2F020.htm&d=9wyTkkYHe0N7GaLerPJJfP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a3f16858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/405/020.htm</a>"},{"pid":"81ce043c95c4533273d1cb88c639c3e22af7a0d3","tid":977351,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3498d4da24779225d8c4e6330b925705abcecc82","tid":977351,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:10:01.000Z","msg":"，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c5ab0edfcf9aebe582474b8d88651194761cca","tid":977351,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\